{"tid":250251,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[一句講哂] 廣西越南泰國 定 西伯利亞鐵路","createTime":"2017-05-20T02:41:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T05:37:48.000Z","uid":88955,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5fe1aeba8697b9f859ccc4b643051dcc2fed0c8c","tid":250251,"uid":88955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T02:41:26.000Z","msg":"大學畢業想瘋狂一次，去半個月-1個月既grad trip, 依家諗左兩條路線，想聽下咁多位巴絲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n路線1: 香港 -&gt; 廣西南寧--&gt; 搭火車落 越南 --&gt; 遊越南 --&gt; 泰國<br />\n<br />\n路線2: 香港--&gt; 北京 --&gt; 坐西伯利亞鐵路 (經蒙古）<br />\n(會係沿途既城市行下玩下） --&gt; 莫斯科<br />\n<br />\n其實呢兩條路線途經既城市都未諗景點，所以想問下咁多位巴絲意見。 或者有冇其他更值得遊既路線？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4092dc3560b9deed51e98a937f80f611d89edf7e","tid":250251,"uid":41434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T02:43:28.000Z","msg":"西伯利亞"},{"pid":"c7954d31b556d1eab93ef532cee648d8ea351d8d","tid":250251,"uid":99989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T02:44:26.000Z","msg":"路線2可以望俄妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe206190880e592f2ba8359e61b80774455343eb","tid":250251,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T02:45:23.000Z","msg":"冬天的冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270310b93634af929cca11b1d362e046151bebe3","tid":250251,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T02:46:38.000Z","msg":"路線1咁近 <br />\n難得咁有紀念性<br />\n去啲特別啲呀麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e8003aa45cd28c83b55d9421502351e7f360329","tid":250251,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T03:18:47.000Z","msg":"西伯利亞鐵道 好似黃翠如識咁多人就正<img src=\"