可以去邊度玩？</blockquote><br />\n如果只係短暫停留都係喺烏蘭巴托hea<br />\n同近近地john tour去gorkhi-terelj national park訓下蒙古包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ntour可以去到烏蘭巴托喺hostel先夾人一齊john"},{"pid":"b323611297e66fb6c4d0e617b3d1d8467f16b5f0","tid":250251,"uid":88955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:46:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好呀！！！ 我睇下d post 先<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲打知蒙古自己一個可以去邊度玩？</blockquote><br />\n如果只係短暫停留都係喺烏蘭巴托hea<br />\n同近近地john tour去gorkhi-terelj national park訓下蒙古包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ntour可以去到烏蘭巴托喺hostel先夾人一齊john</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好提議！！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbdc01f9bd17d824b3bde0e04a75f0fe87879e8e","tid":250251,"uid":88955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:47:08.000Z","msg":"咁西伯利亞鐵路沿途既城市有咩好去處？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea0816dea7de755ead67e859d7fcecac906e8763","tid":250251,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:53:16.000Z","msg":"路線一唔覺有幾瘋狂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b65cedea5e33628a4ac6d7859e405f8ae15c62","tid":250251,"uid":88955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T17:07:23.000Z","msg":"自己一個去安唔安全？"},{"pid":"8322d4507fe516f8dc2cd1f9923b115d8fc2ad04","tid":250251,"uid":55923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T17:15:09.000Z","msg":"路線二都好多香港人去到爛<br />\n如果剩係為咗個湖同火車, <br />\n不如坐飛機去然後搭吓electrichka"},{"pid":"bc359317350af7d6f70b240856a8f09a8b8eaf58","tid":250251,"uid":31725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T17:17:09.000Z","msg":"路線2路線2路線2"},{"pid":"6612c03b427268a8f39df56466d1c574b4606786","tid":250251,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T04:36:13.000Z","msg":"坐火車上蒙古玩，玩完再坐西伯利亞鐵路去莫斯科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n舊年grad trip 我淨係由烏蘭巴托坐到俄羅斯既伊爾庫次克<br />\n蒙古玩左戈壁團、跟住俄羅斯去左伊市同貝加爾湖<br />\n本來計劃坐埋去莫斯科但冇時間咁做，好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  以後都唔知有冇時間同精力咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6981f246b0adb1987c22f7ce40b7904070cf812c","tid":250251,"uid":7442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:20:35.000Z","msg":"玩後者要幾耐 1個月夠唔夠玩哂?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285416442ffd0f67b7f6e4c6c78774afba2b28b1","tid":250251,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:57:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩後者要幾耐 1個月夠唔夠玩哂?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得! 你總站係莫斯科"},{"pid":"4e5983f772e32272ebf324410280508a09bd78cd","tid":250251,"uid":83920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T08:55:15.000Z","msg":"西伯利亞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90bf0a88644ec2c945ae8dfa7267a3800d01e2c1","tid":250251,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:28:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己一個去安唔安全？</blockquote><br />\n安全就唔瘋狂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c1572f60753b90b6ca6513b638148fbfdb05bbd","tid":250251,"uid":88955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T03:12:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自己一個去安唔安全？</blockquote><br />\n安全就唔瘋狂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打講得岩！"}]}